reviewText: Amazing DVD it was worth every penny. This woman is a great teacher and she makes you feel as if she is mentoring you. She is truly gifted. I discovered this gifted gem on YouTube and I was impressed with her method of teaching the tarot in a way I have never seen before on there. If you want to learn the tarot in depth and in detail buy this DVD. Thank you Rhiannon for this awesome material. This is coming from a fan from the USA.
